{"tid":1742000,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【公投】星期日區選 唔該大家搵個共識 著咩顏色衫！十萬火急！","createTime":"2019-11-20T14:53:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T09:56:30.000Z","uid":167548,"like":11,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"900d0dd140551fca3a68940e9f3e6fe77b6dd31f","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:53:42.000Z","msg":"【政情】建制選情低位反彈 泛民高位回落<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezdBHS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezdBHS</a><br />\n個人見解+其他巴打分析：<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#2010LV&bull;</span>19 分鐘前<br />\n搵警察開箱<br />\n<br />\n投左泛民既都畫花佢, 作廢<br />\n<br />\n封點投站, 市民想監票就告暴動罪<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n大家應該知道, 區選選舉舞弊並非一朝一夕！<br />\n近排見唔少TG message叫大家扮建制著非黑衫, 等佢地自已睇錯種錯票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但是你地有冇諗過對家為所欲為？佢點完票前, 加大量假選票都沒問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地有兩百萬人(20萬未滿18歲)都有180萬人, 只有佢地做返選民責任贏硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地是唔是ON9架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n扮建制, 你地幫緊對家知唔知啊！<br />\n你地幫緊佢地作數據嘅可信性！<br />\n佢掉你走曬你地o的票都得啊！<br />\n我記得雲海fb講過佢試過想跟票箱, 都比POPO兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今個星期日想贏到盡, 要做3樣野！<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1. 著黑衫去投票！<br />\n2. 叫你班港豬淺黃朋友去投</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>3. 未夠18歲手足組團去各大票站點黑衫人數！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黑衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">非黑衫</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n求大家呢個好緊急, 幫手forward出去！<br />\n千祈唔好扮建制！<br />\n千祈唔好扮建制！<br />\n千祈唔好扮建制！<br />\n我地勝在人夠人, 如果票站人人著黑衫, 佢點樣作數啊！<br />\n得呢個方法可以自保！即使輸左民意一樣我地嘅！<br />\n我地要搞到班廢老懷疑人生！<br />\n同埋非選民幫手去投票！"},{"pid":"195509438bd73b22da3cbb8a6b61de751290b94f","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:54:25.000Z","msg":"幫手推+share去TG公海"},{"pid":"f65a3d0d49fe2031be67c461ebf5ee10df342021","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:55:12.000Z","msg":"求指出錯誤 個人睇法著非黑衫 百害而無一利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc8515b56610b68cda4c03c7fac8638f130b099","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:56:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">千祈唔好扮建制！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"27196550e4059aebb48e692cfffc144268b7c424","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"票箱可以唔見, 選票可以做假, <br />\n但是11.24各大票站<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黑衣人龍</span></span></strong>就是鐵證"},{"pid":"9cd7e87bceeec87704358bb8d2c7b35f071b8b9e","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:58:11.000Z","msg":"唔該大家諗下, 你扮建制是唔是傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ac5e761d02a3a9463813ce0e1f128bf95ca193","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"痴線, 今鋪好大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地是要假設佢用曬下三流手段<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eaa709f062f2953ae39c6d683fd1b38eae08a3d","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:59:38.000Z","msg":"求下大家睇完先比LIKE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c63aac63c171b78a0dc77c327605d63daa2aa6e","tid":1742000,"uid":167548,"like":0,"di